NUMBER 1023
NAME Zorha's Rec Room
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Lush, vibrant palm trees sway pleasantly in a gentle magical breeze that
swirls throughout this chamber. The walls and floor of the chamber are a
polished white marble, striated by streaks of light blue. The six palm trees
surround a sparkling, oval pool filled with crystal blue water that laps
gently against the smooth sides. Off to one side of the pool are thick
padded mats, used by the Queen for her training. A blue marble arch leads
off towards the bedchamber, and a white arch leads back to the Common Room.
*DESCRIPTION_END
