NUMBER 1025
NAME Zorha's sitting room
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
This small comfortable room contains plush, overstuffed chairs and couches.
A richly woven rug, its soft, colorful fibers threaded into an intricate
portrayal of a beautiful white mare. Atop the rug is a smooth, white marble
table with two inviting chairs placed next to its polished presence. The
painting of an imposing figure gazes down upon the entire room from its
position above a red brick fireplace. A white door, carved with the crest
of the Kentaurus family is on the north wall, and a white marble arch leads
out to the recreation room. A new opening has been placed above the arch
leading to the recreation room.
*DESCRIPTION_END
