NUMBER 1026
NAME Royal Bedchamber
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Royal blue velvet drapes hang from the top of this rooms centerpiece, a
large oval double bed. Silk bedsheets, bearing the sewn crest of
Queen Zorha, lie atop the incredibly soft mattress. Numerous
pillows are scattered across the breadth of the bed, lending the final
touch to the exquisite sleeping spot. A tall mirror sits atop a deeply
stained oak desk with numerous drawers. Two porcelain vases sit on either
side of the mirror, refreshed with colorful flowers each morning. A white
door leads out to the Queen's sitting room, and a black door has been
locked and barred from anyone attempting to enter.
*DESCRIPTION_END
