CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The bright walls in this tiny chamber are gaily painted with various small
and cuddly animals. Numerous stuffed bears and other toys for tiny tots
are scattered throughout the room, mostly surrounding the beautiful mirmach
cradle that is the centerpiece of the room. A soothing, warm light fills the
room, along with faint sylvan music.
*DESCRIPTION_END
