ITEM 0 1911 ADJ1=196
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The four corners of the cradle are carved to resemble rearing unicorns that
glow with a comforting light. Painted on the center board of the cradle is
the highly stylized seal of the Royal Family. Numerous silks and pillows are
inside the cradle, meant to make the tiny child comfortable.
*DESCRIPTION_END
