NUMBER 376
NAME Palace, fountain
MONSTER_GROUP 15
OUTDOOR_OTHER
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
This tree-enclosed grove contains a blue stone fountain that has an
majestic looking dolphin as it's centerpiece. Stone benches surround
the fountain. The dolphin shoots an continous stream of water out of
it's mouth that catches the light and then cascade down into the pool
below. It is an beautiful sight, and there are many who come here to
meditate in the peace that the grove offers.
*DESCRIPTION_END
